{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/decrease-the-opacity-of-an-element","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Smanjite neprozirnost elementa","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><code>opacity</code> svojstvo u CSS se koristi za podešavanje providnosti, odnosno neprovidnosti za element.</p>\n<blockquote>Vrednost 1 je potpuno neprovidna, što nije providna uopšte.<br>Vrednost 0.5 je poluprovidna.<br>Vrednost 0 je potpuno providna.</blockquote>\n<p>Data vrednost će se primeniti na ceo element, bilo da je to slika sa određenom providnošću, ili boje prednjeg i pozadinskog plana za deo teksta.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d781c367417b2b2512abf","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Postavite <code>opacity</code> sidrenih tagova na 0.7 koristeći klasu <code>links</code> za selektovanje tih tagova.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/c7aKqu4","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301055,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/decrease-the-opacity-of-an-element"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  h4 {\n    text-align: center;\n    background-color: rgba(45, 45, 45, 0.1);\n    padding: 10px;\n    font-size: 27px;\n  }\n  p {\n    text-align: justify;\n  }\n  .links {\n    text-align: left;\n    color: black;\n\n  }\n  #thumbnail {\n    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.19), 0 6px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.23);\n  }\n  .fullCard {\n    width: 245px;\n    border: 1px solid #ccc;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    margin: 10px 5px;\n    padding: 4px;\n  }\n  .cardContent {\n    padding: 10px;\n  }\n  .cardText {\n    margin-b